high_descs: Go forward and stand in front of the toaster.
Pick up the potato from the counter.
Turn left to face the microwave.
Open the cabinet above and to the right of the microwave and put the potato in the bowl.
Pick up the bowl with the potato in it.
Look down at the microwave.
Put the bowl and potato in the microwave and heat it.
anns.task_desc: Heat a potato in the microwave.

high_descs: Take a step so you are clear of the counter on your right and then walk to the toaster you see in front of you.
Pick up the potato that's to the left of the toaster.
Turn left to face the microwave and look at the cabinets above it.
Open the right cabinet and put the potato in the clear glass bowl.
Pick up the bowl with the potato in it and close the cabinet.
Look down at the microwave now.
Put the bowl in the microwave and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a potato in it in the microwave.

high_descs: Go past the fridge on the left to the counter by the toaster.
Pick up the potato behind the toaster on the counter.
Turn and go to the cabinet to the right of the fridge.
Put the potato in the bowl in the right side cabinet.
Pick up the bowl with the potato inside in the cabinet.
Go to the microwave.
Put the bowl with the potato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a potato inside in the microwave.
